 />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去facebook，歡迎喺facebook pm呢個page: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=562e0762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"3a8fd2b32801738a44049df4c84de04f4133ecf1","tid":1362582,"uid":61938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"216cee60421cf16897adee6c4068d0eecf87474d","tid":1362582,"uid":248177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75769b3ac8a4540c1a04548527d72e0b1705b4e8","tid":1362582,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abc2928981640d150b11e911ade409a34331f166","tid":1362582,"uid":248177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:49:08.000Z","msg":"其實係每日都要mark請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係專登mark果日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:57:17.000Z","msg":"有scso 12/6都放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"perm我唔知<br />\n但NCSC每個月attendance record都要比RM/Stat簽先出到糧<br />\n所以唔係突登點名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:29:29.000Z","msg":"CPI of course la."},{"pid":"6c25f5282837e7fc11f50e7a09751c524718c0f7","tid":1362582,"uid":265314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:35:59.000Z","msg":"一個已經好多"},{"pid":"944fa2f54454658beb8a9e6fff591ee1b2fd6c65","tid":1362582,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"勇敢！<img src=\"/a